OL,3,CAssembly recall over special school
OL,4,Csummer scheme U-turn
OL,6,FMLAs have been called back to Stormont
OL,7,Ffrom their Easter recess to discuss
OL,8,Fthe fallout over special school summer
OL,9,Fschemes.
OL,11,FAn Alliance petition last Friday to
OL,12,Frecall Stormont was successful after
OL,13,Fit emerged that the schemes, which
OL,14,Fprovide support for children with
OL,15,Fadditional needs over the summer,
OL,16,Fwould not go ahead due to a lack of
OL,17,Fnursing support. However, in a joint
OL,18,Fstatement last Friday the Education
OL,19,Fand Health Ministers said they had
OL,20,Ffound a way for the schemes to go
OL,21,Fahead.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
