OL,3,CAssembly recall over special school
OL,4,Csummer scheme U-turn
OL,6,FIt emerged last Thursday (26th March)
OL,7,Fthat the schemes would not go ahead in
OL,8,F2026 over concerns about the
OL,9,Fhealthcare available for pupils.
OL,11,FA resolution was announced on Friday
OL,12,Fafternoon following engagement between
OL,13,Fthe Department of Health, the
OL,14,FDepartment of Education and the
OL,15,FEducation Authority (EA).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
