OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774991532
OL,3,CAssembly recall over special school
OL,4,Csummer scheme U-turn
OL,6,FThe Department of Health is to provide
OL,7,Fnursing support at each special school
OL,8,Fsummer scheme site ` after saying last
OL,9,FThursday that onsite registered
OL,10,Fnursing provision was not needed at
OL,11,Fall sites.
OL,13,FThe U-turn has been welcomed by MLAs,
OL,14,Fsome of whom have asked the Health
OL,15,FMinister Mike Nesbitt and Education
OL,16,FMinister Paul Givan to provide
OL,17,Fexplanations on how the problem
OL,18,Funfolded.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
