PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774991532
OL,3,CAssembly recall over special school
OL,4,Csummer scheme U-turn
OL,6,F"This represents a workable solution
OL,7,Fthat will enable special school summer
OL,8,Fschemes to be held this year," the EA
OL,9,Fsaid in a statement on Friday.
OL,11,F"The overriding priority of everyone
OL,12,Fconcerned remains the safety and well-
OL,13,Fbeing of children and young people,
OL,14,Fand EA will continue to work with
OL,15,Fspecial school principals to urgently
OL,16,Fprioritise planning for the summer
OL,17,Fschemes.
